-- Spain's Win Against Netherlands Was Most-Watched World Cup Game, ESPN Says
-- Vivek Shankar
-- 2010-07-12T21:12:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/spain-s-win-against-netherlands-was-most-watched-world-cup-game-espn-says.html

          
          
             The FIFA World Cup final, in which
Spain beat the Netherlands 1-0, was the most-watched men’s World
Cup game ever, Walt Disney Co.’s ESPN said in an e-mail, citing
data from Nielsen Co. The game was telecast on Disney’s ABC
network.  
          
          


  


        